  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the best jeans bands in India?",
  "response": "In India, there are several popular and trusted brands for jeans, catering to a wide range of styles, budgets, and preferences. Here are some of the best jeans brands in India:\n\n### **Premium Brands**\n1. **Levi's**  \n   Known for its classic and durable denim, Levi's is a global leader in the jeans market. It offers a variety of fits and styles.\n\n2. **Wrangler**  \n   Famous for its rugged and durable jeans, Wrangler is a favorite among those looking for quality and comfort.\n\n3. **Lee**  \n   Lee offers comfortable and stylish jeans with a focus on modern fits and designs.\n\n4. **Pepe Jeans**  \n   A premium brand with trendy designs, Pepe Jeans is popular among fashion-conscious individuals.\n\n5. **Tommy Hilfiger**  \n   Known for its premium and stylish denim, Tommy Hilfiger offers a blend of classic and contemporary designs.\n\n---\n\n### **Mid-Range Brands**\n6. **Jack & Jones**  \n   A Danish brand, Jack & Jones offers stylish and affordable jeans with a European flair.\n\n7. **Spykar**  \n   A homegrown brand, Spykar is known for its trendy and budget-friendly jeans.\n\n8. **Flying Machine**  \n   Offering a mix of casual and stylish denim, Flying Machine is a popular choice among youth.\n\n9. **Killer Jeans**  \n   Known for its edgy and youthful designs, Killer Jeans is a favorite in the Indian market.\n\n10. **Denizen by Levi's**  \n    A more affordable line by Levi's, Denizen offers good-quality jeans at a lower price point.\n\n---\n\n### **Budget-Friendly Brands**\n11. **Max Fashion**  \n    Max offers affordable and stylish jeans for men, women, and kids.\n\n12. **Roadster**  \n    A brand by Myntra, Roadster offers trendy and budget-friendly jeans.\n\n13. **H&M**  \n    Known for its trendy and affordable fashion, H&M offers a wide range of jeans for all age groups.\n\n14. **Reliance Trends**  \n    A popular Indian brand, Reliance Trends offers affordable and stylish jeans.\n\n15. **Bewakoof**  \n    A youth-centric brand, Bewakoof offers quirky and budget-friendly jeans.\n\n---\n\n### **Luxury Brands**\n16. **Armani Jeans**  \n    A luxury brand offering high-end denim with sophisticated designs.\n\n17. **Diesel**  \n    Known for its premium and edgy designs, Diesel is a favorite among fashion enthusiasts.\n\n---\n\n### **Ethnic and Sustainable Options**\n18. **Bhaane**  \n    Offers sustainable and stylish denim options.\n\n19. **DNMX**  \n    Focuses on affordable and trendy denim for the Indian market.\n\n20. **Numero Uno**  \n    Known for its casual and chic denim collection.\n\n---\n\nThese brands cater to different tastes, budgets, and preferences, making them popular choices for jeans in India.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
